  <brief_title>Investigation on the Value of Bilateral Index (BIS) Monitoring for Magnetic Seizure Versus Electroconvulsive Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Bilateral Bispectral Index Monitoring During and After Electroconvulsive Therapy Compared With Magnetic Seizure Therapy for Treatment-resistant Depression</official_title>
  <sponsors>
